WEBVTT

00:00.151 --> 00:01.599
Hi, I'm David.

00:01.903 --> 00:03.334
What is your name?

00:03.915 --> 00:06.355
My Korean name is Jun Hyung.

00:06.973 --> 00:08.509
My friends call me just Jun.

00:09.097 --> 00:10.416
Feel free to call me Jun.

00:10.789 --> 00:11.634
I see.

00:12.123 --> 00:13.438
Where do you live, Jun?

00:13.825 --> 00:15.023
I live in Busan.

00:15.323 --> 00:16.985
Have you been to Busan before?

00:17.235 --> 00:20.347
Yes, but it was a long time ago.

00:20.975 --> 00:22.264
Where do you work, David?

00:22.603 --> 00:24.930
I work at the Grand Restaurant.

00:25.181 --> 00:26.567
I'm a restaurant manager.

00:26.766 --> 00:27.278
Really?

00:27.610 --> 00:28.645
That sounds nice!

00:29.056 --> 00:30.685
I should eat out there sometime.

